    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then roughly chop your <strong>spring onions</strong> into batons</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Finely slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1678188684071-x200.jpg",
