          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1678188693433-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer everything to a plate (save the pan!) and set aside until serving – this is your <strong>salt & pepper duck</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>cooled rice</strong>, <strong>blanched peas</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> then stir everything together until combined and cook for 2-3 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1678188700309-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
