          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1678188700309-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once combined, push the rice to one side of the pan and crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into the other side</p><p>Stir the<strong> egg[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>with a wooden spoon to break the yolk[s] and cook for 1-2 min until it resembles scrambled egg, then mix it all through the rice – this is your <strong>egg fried rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
