            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1678188704890-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> salt & pepper duck</strong> over the <strong>egg fried rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
